texts.text: TU37 was a version of Xbox 360 Edition released on June 26, 2016.[1] [edit]
Fixed an issue stopping people joining a public Battle mini game if a player in the game had UGC settings of "Friends Only" on.
"Minecraft: Xbox 360 Edition Patch change logs" – Minecraft Forum, June 26, 2016.
